page_title: Azure OpenAI Service API version retirement
page_description: Learn more about API version retirement in Azure OpenAI Services.
chunk_content: Updating API versionsWe recommend first testing the upgrade to new API versions to confirm there's no impact to your application from the API update before making the change globally across your environment.If you're using the OpenAI Python client library or the REST API, you'll need to update your code directly to the latest preview API version.If you're using one of the Azure OpenAI SDKs for C#, Go, Java, or JavaScript you'll instead need to update to the latest version of the SDK. Each SDK release is hardcoded to work with specific versions of the Azure OpenAI API.
